did.abstract:
Collection consists of an assortment of
        correspondence, fragments, and notes from Thomas and Jane Welsh Carlyle. Correspondents
        include Carlyle's secretary, Henry Larkin; John Fergusson; Thomas Murray; Basil Montagu;
        Bryan Waller Procter ("Barry Cornwall"); Henrietta Maria Stanley; Ralph Waldo Emerson;
        Thomas Erskine; Richard Owen; Frederic Chapman; William McCall; and John Reuben
        Thomas.
